{"tid":1524101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"義士們, 除咗5大訴求, 請對自己做到5大要求","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:23.000Z","uid":56546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd0be028e879b7118d72f9712c3818963d7439c","tid":1524101,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 不戀戰<br />\n2. 不留手<br />\n3. 不被捕<br />\n4. 不失去冷靜<br />\n5. 不再受大愛左膠心態影響</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面頭4點唔想講咁多<br />\n<br />\n但特別第5點<br />\n本身運動一開始其實大家都係大約5 5 波<br />\n警察都驚自己做得太過火會俾人私了<br />\n<br />\n但點解近期對面越黎越大膽<br />\n就係知你地永遠有班人要道德光環<br />\n<br />\n捉到鬼又唔打<br />\n警察大搖大擺得3 4隻兵拉人<br />\n明明成條村都係自己人, 都無人郁手救人<br />\n例子真係太多<br />\n次次頂盡就係話文宣核彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大佬呢個世界無人會幫loser<br />\n你想外國幫你<br />\n都要俾人見到你地有機會贏先得架"},{"pid":"737eb6f270582eef7cb923728a513e924e165170","tid":1524101,"uid":308567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70myprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=2f2d3af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"31c6a02c81330c6e8c78efaf659a5a7ad3d6bdbb","tid":1524101,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac4067e3c0618fa87f0e0e30869b89e409e3fa6","tid":1524101,"uid":92277,"like":0